709
00:36:47,250 --> 00:36:48,170
I wasn't there.

710
00:36:47,430 --> 00:36:50,180
♫I waited and it came♫

711
00:36:48,710 --> 00:36:49,490
Otherwise,

712
00:36:49,830 --> 00:36:51,720
