00:37:55,650 --> 00:38:02,960
♫This long journey where one shadow became two♫

741
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:56,550
A gift in return.

742
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:06,160
♫At the end of the road, it's a dream♫

743
00:38:04,630 --> 00:38:05,260
For you.

